        <span class="text-white">キャンペーン中</span>
        <span class="text-white/45">／</span>
        <span class="text-[#f2b04a] font-black">買取金額10%UP</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[4.82cqw] font-black leading-[1.24] mt-[1cqw] text-white" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);">
        名古屋の家具・家電<br />
        出張買取・<span class="text-terra-light">高価買取</span>
