        <span class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[1.63cqw] font-bold leading-[1.2] px-[1.7cqw] py-[0.6cqw] rounded-full border border-white/30 whitespace-nowrap">査定0円</span>
        <span class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[1.63cqw] font-bold leading-[1.2] px-[1.7cqw] py-[0.6cqw] rounded-full border border-white/30 whitespace-nowrap">最短即日</span>
