          <span class="text-white font-black text-[6.3cqw] leading-none tracking-tight whitespace-nowrap" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);">052-990-3968</span>
        </span>
        <span class="block bg-[#8a2f0e] text-center text-white font-bold text-[2.15cqw] py-[0.6cqw] tracking-wide">受付中 9:00〜21:00・年中無休</span>
      </a>
      <p class="text-center text-white/95 text-[1.82cqw] font-medium leading-[1.5] mt-[1.38cqw]" style="text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);">査定だけのお電話、歓迎です。</p>
      <a href="https://lin.ee/j4wK9IM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-glow-line flex items-center justify-center gap-[1cqw] bg-[#3eb168] hover:brightness-110 text-white font-bold text-[1.95cqw] min-h-[4.56cqw] w-[23cqw] mx-auto rounded-[1.1cqw] mt-[0.6cqw] text-center shadow-lg transition-all">
